    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/106bd75e84a40c8948d245d0ba4c95d8.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=72 /></span>大发明家莉斯塔居住在小镇里，过着安宁恬静的生活。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >但她原本平静的生活却被一场突如其来的变故打破——镇子里的机器人集体发起狂来，将小镇中的设施破坏殆尽。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >作为机器人专家，莉斯塔和她的好友克丽耶义不容辞地踏上了冒险。她们能否顺利解决眼下的危机，找到隐藏在这场变故背后的真相呢？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/8a2e919cb292367484fdeffc0c1db12d.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=72 /></span>在这部横版过关游戏中前进吧！每种敌人都有不同的攻击方式，根据敌人的类型制定不同的作战策略，用手中的枪消灭敌人吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/00ea79eea1f971d62bd9ee3b3c9a7aa9.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=72 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/5e91ee2480ed4285fee6e45f006746d1.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/bec2ea1abdfd4453a72a20c8a17893c2.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=399 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/066f025f06e5f88ff7825a46f5a0f935.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=399 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2219800/extras/37bdbcb26b0c7e4e3c44d43c89f73d85.avif?t=1749284239\" width=616 height=72 /></span><strong>激动人心的BOSS战</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每层地图都包含一名拥有独特能力的BOSS级敌人。使用各种技巧突破他们的防线，继续推进剧情吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>多种多样的武器</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本作包含了数种可解锁的武器。这些武器拥有不同的特色与功能，收集得越多，战斗也会随之越容易！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>妙趣横生的剧情</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >逐步发掘机器人失控事件的真相，查明芙蕾泽萝真正的动机吧！</p>",
